---
---
<section id="pillars" aria-labelledby="pillars-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="pillars-header">
      <div class="section-label" data-i18n="pillars.label">What We Do</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="pillars-heading" data-i18n="pillars.title">Three pillars.<br>One cohesive system.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub" data-i18n="pillars.sub">Every engagement covers what actually moves the needle — nothing else.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <!-- Pillar 1 -->
      <article class="pillar-card reveal" aria-labelledby="pillar-1-title">
        <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title" id="pillar-1-title" data-i18n="pillars.p1.title">Brand &amp; Packaging</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc" data-i18n="pillars.p1.desc">Identity that earns attention before a single word is read.</p>
        <ul class="pillar-list" role="list">
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p1.item1">Brand identity systems</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p1.item2">Packaging design</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p1.item3">Product storytelling</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p1.item4">Visual systems &amp; guidelines</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" data-i18n="pillars.cta">Start a Project</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Pillar 2 -->
      <article class="pillar-card reveal reveal-delay-1" aria-labelledby="pillar-2-title">
        <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title" id="pillar-2-title" data-i18n="pillars.p2.title">Ecommerce Engineering</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc" data-i18n="pillars.p2.desc">Stores built to convert — not just to exist.</p>
        <ul class="pillar-list" role="list">
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p2.item1">Shopify &amp; WooCommerce builds</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p2.item2">High-converting PDP systems</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p2.item3">Pixel &amp; analytics setup (Meta, GA4, TikTok)</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p2.item4">Performance &amp; SEO foundation</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" data-i18n="pillars.cta">Start a Project</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Pillar 3 -->
      <article class="pillar-card reveal reveal-delay-2" aria-labelledby="pillar-3-title">
        <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title" id="pillar-3-title" data-i18n="pillars.p3.title">Growth Systems</h3>
        <p class="pillar-desc" data-i18n="pillars.p3.desc">The infrastructure that compounds revenue over time.</p>
        <ul class="pillar-list" role="list">
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p3.item1">Email &amp; SMS flows</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p3.item2">Post-purchase optimization</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p3.item3">Loyalty &amp; referral systems</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p3.item4">Affiliate infrastructure</li>
          <li data-i18n="pillars.p3.item5">CRO sprints</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" data-i18n="pillars.cta">Start a Project</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
